a.xlink:title: MOM_grid_init initializes the ocean grid array sizes and grid memory.
set_grid_metrics is used to set the primary values in the model's horizontal grid. The bathymetry, land-sea mask and any restricted channel widths are not know yet, so these are set later.
hor_index_init sets various index values in a hor_index_type.
Allocate memory used by the ocean_grid_type and related structures.
Writes a message about entering a subroutine if call tree reporting is active.
Writes a message about leaving a subroutine if call tree reporting is active.
set_derived_metrics calculates metric terms that are derived from other metrics.
grid_metrics_chksum performs a set of checksums on metrics on the grid for debugging.
extrapolate_metric extrapolates missing metric data into all the halo regions.
